[
  {
    "scene": "TitleScene",
    "file": "01-title.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "歡迎來到誰讓他煉器的！第三章，第一集，秘境探索。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "低語洞窟的任務完成後，邏輯修正小組的名聲傳遍了問道宗——當然，是「禍害」那種名聲。長老決定把他們派去參加五年一次的宗門秘境探索，希望他們在別人面前丟臉。但周墨對這次任務充滿期待——因為秘境裡有大量上古陣法，簡直是工程師的天堂。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene1",
    "file": "02-content1.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "宗門秘境入口，五大宗門齊聚。各派精英弟子正在研究上古禁制的破解方法。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "這次秘境探索，你們三個給我安分點。別丟問道宗的臉。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "長老放心，我帶了五份投降表，涵蓋所有可能的宗門。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我帶了論文草稿——「秘境環境對單身光環的影響研究」。如果遇到女修，這是很好的數據採集機會。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……你們能不能有一次正常的準備？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "長老，我準備了「雷射切割陣法」。根據古籍記載，這個秘境的禁制是三千年前的陣法構建，結構規律性很高，可以用線性切割的方式高效破解。"
      },
      {
        "character": "elder",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "你說的是那個……看起來像一根會發光的筷子一樣的東西？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "那是「聚焦式靈氣切割陣法發射器」。我簡稱它「雷射筆」。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "看起來確實像一支筆。一支會把東西切開的筆。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "記錄：周墨又造了一個危險的東西。這是第幾次了？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "這不是危險，這是效率。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "ContentScene2",
    "file": "03-content2.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "秘境內部。其他宗門的弟子們正在用各種方法破解禁制——有人用符咒，有人用劍氣，有人用陣盤。進度：零。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "那個天劍宗的首席弟子已經砍了三十七劍了。禁制連個痕跡都沒有。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我在旁邊觀察了。他的臉越來越紅。我覺得他快要——"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "閃開。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "周墨按下雷射筆的按鈕。一道筆直的靈氣光束射出——"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "禁制。被切成了兩半。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……就這樣？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "就這樣。三千年前的陣法結構是單層線性排列，沒有冗餘設計。一個工程師的基本常識：永遠不要信任沒有備份的系統。"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "但是周墨……你好像把所有禁制都切斷了。不只是入口這個——整座秘境的禁制系統。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "嗯，雷射筆的切割範圍確實沒有設定邊界。我記得我加了方向控制……等等，我忘了加方向控制。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "整座秘境震動。牆壁上浮現出上古文字：「警告——禁制系統已離線——保護機制啟動——自毀倒數：一百八十息。」"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "一百八十息？那是我們能活多久的意思嗎？"
      },
      {
        "character": "luyang",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "我的投降表能遞給上古大能的保護機制嗎？"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "冷靜。這只是一個計時觸發的自動防禦協議。我來看看能不能找到……出口。"
      },
      {
        "character": "mengjingzhou",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "出口也被你切斷了。你看，那個門已經變成兩半了。"
      },
      {
        "character": "zhoumo",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "……這是一個需要優化的設計缺陷。"
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "scene": "OutroScene",
    "file": "04-outro.wav",
    "segments": [
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "感謝收看誰讓他煉器的！第三章第一集，秘境探索。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "邏輯修正小組成功進入了秘境——然後成功觸發了自毀倒數。周墨的雷射筆效率很高，但忘了加方向限制，導致出口也被切斷了。現在問題很簡單：在一百八十息之內，找到一個不存在的出口。"
      },
      {
        "character": "narrator",
        "voice": "uncle_fu",
        "voiceDescription": {
          "voice": "uncle_fu",
          "gender": "male",
          "accent": "standard Mandarin"
        },
        "text": "下集預告：邏輯修正小組在自毀倒計時中瘋狂找出口，結果發現秘境的核心藏著一個更大的秘密——上古大能設計這個秘境的真正目的，竟然是為了測試「後人的智商」。"
      }
    ]
  }
]
